      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "只有死人才用得着这么样一个坑，难道他想死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "看样子好像是的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "像他这么样一个人，为什么想死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "因为他也跟我们一样，也接到一封信，叫他今天到这里来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "那封信也是碧玉夫人给他的！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "一定是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "碧玉夫人叫我们到这里来，是为了要在我们四个人之中，选一个女婿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "碧玉夫人是天下公认的第一位高人，碧玉山庄中，每个人都是天香国色，我接到那封信时，高兴得连觉都睡不着。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "我可以想得到。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "如果她选中我做女婿，我说不定会高兴得发疯。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "你最好不要疯，碧玉夫人绝不会要一个疯子做女婿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "她会不会要一个死人做女婿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "更不会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "那么我们这位邱公子，好好的为什么想死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "因为他是个痴情的人，而且已经跟一位美丽的姑娘，订下了生死不渝的山盟海誓。如果碧玉夫人选中他做女婿，他就没法子和那位姑娘共偕白首了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "所以只要碧玉夫人一选中他做女婿，他就决心死在这里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "这件事还有另一种说法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "什么说法。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "碧玉夫人是不是一定会看见这个坑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "这么大一个坑，想要看不见，恐怕都很难。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "她看见了这个坑，就知道邱公子已经抱定了决死之心，说不定就会放过他，选我做碧玉山庄的姑爷了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "text": "你真是个聪明人，聪明人的想法，总是跟别人不一样的，跟痴情人更不一样。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "痴情人也未必就不是聪明人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "你怎么知道这件事的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "你想不到我会知道这件事？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自己也想不到，只可惜那位美丽的姑娘……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "text": "你是不是……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_hong_ye",
      "speaker_name": "沈红叶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来还是我的运气比你好，我就站在这个坑旁……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    }
